|n| = |v| = \sqrt{v_x^2+v_y^2}
\hat n = \frac{n}{|n|} = \left({\frac{v_y}{\scriptstyle \sqrt{v_x^2+v_y^2}},\ \frac{-v_x}{\scriptstyle \sqrt{v_x^2+v_y^2}}}\right).
